---
title: Carla Hall's Summery Lemon Chicken with Tarragon Chimichurri
description: You’re a key ingredient in the fight against AIDS. To that end, HelloFresh has teamed up with chef Carla Hall to bring you her Summery Lemon Chicken recipe, which was specially crafted for EAT (RED) SAVE LIVES. Built around pan-cooked chicken breasts, fluffy couscous, and a kale salad with citrus, its flavors truly soar when you add the garlicky tarragon chimichurri sauce. According to Carla, it’s an “easy-to-make, delicious recipe for you and your loved ones to enjoy.”
